Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.34,0:00:04.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先向大家说声 谢谢啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.55,0:00:05.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好突然哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.70,0:00:07.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是 谢谢啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.60,0:00:09.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在看水星领航员的各位观众
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.40,0:00:12.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏了各位给我们带来的暖风
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.87,0:00:13.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.07,0:00:15.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超级感谢的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.44,0:00:16.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是美好的奇迹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.05,0:00:19.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,微妙的让人害羞的台词 禁止
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.19,0:00:20.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.95,0:00:26.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小爱 持续到昨天的雨终于停歇了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.63,0:00:28.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是个非常好的天气
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.12,0:00:32.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说如此 但因为艾莉西亚前辈有事要出去一天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.30,0:00:34.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天就临时歇业了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.82,0:00:38.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 蓝华有工作
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.10,0:00:40.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱丽丝要上学
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.11,0:00:42.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此这般
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.28,0:00:46.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和亚利亚社长也决定出门去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.56,0:02:37.53,TITLE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,0)\pos(433,290)\blur9\be1\fsp2}那个 小小的秘密之地…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.01,0:02:49.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这附近全是住宅区
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.23,0:02:52.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此在做导游的时候不会到这边来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.37,0:02:56.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但也是新威尼斯的另一副面容
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.37,0:02:59.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论何时来都是不变的风景
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.67,0:03:05.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雨一直下到昨天才停
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.14,0:03:08.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里一定很值得期待
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.23,0:03:13.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去了哦 亚利亚社长
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.10,0:03:17.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一二 嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.08,0:03:21.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然有好多好多衣服呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.10,0:03:28.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 这里有更多哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.81,0:03:47.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晾着的衣服舒舒服服地在空中畅游呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.23,0:03:52.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.92,0:03:55.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么就把衣服弄脏了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.87,0:03:58.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为那里有水坑…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.93,0:04:01.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才刚洗完衣服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.46,0:04:03.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.47,0:04:06.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空中邮递员哥哥还夸我很活泼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.15,0:04:10.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那是活泼过头了啦 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.23,0:04:43.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.69,0:05:09.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从这里也能看到钟楼呢 亚利亚社长
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.04,0:05:12.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚利亚社长？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.73,0:05:29.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚利亚社长…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.43,0:05:39.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 请用
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.96,0:05:53.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里的风景
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.72,0:05:57.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从我来到这个城市 就没有改变过呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.55,0:06:11.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子有点饿了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.08,0:06:17.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我们去吃午饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.10,0:06:23.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 对了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.68,0:06:25.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如我们去吃那个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.22,0:06:27.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.06,0:06:30.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次在附近的店里吃到的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.64,0:06:33.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个让人兴奋紧张的料理啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.98,0:06:37.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.50,0:06:41.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 出发
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.50,0:06:46.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 是二人份吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.51,0:06:48.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.95,0:06:51.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了 请稍等
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.92,0:06:54.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,期待期待 期待期待
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.70,0:06:58.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.52,0:07:13.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样 很好玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.90,0:07:20.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从小时候起就喜欢把这家店的粗粮饼堆得像火山一样吃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.76,0:07:23.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 好有历史感哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.63,0:07:27.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我开动啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.98,0:07:30.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次来的时候我们试试那个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.48,0:07:33.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让您久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.96,0:07:34.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.41,0:07:37.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是弹面
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.39,0:07:40.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,期待期待 期待期待
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.30,0:07:50.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,期待期待 期待期待 期待期待 期待期待
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.37,0:07:59.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 请用
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.72,0:08:00.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.99,0:08:08.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好玩～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.90,0:08:11.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.40,0:08:20.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.24,0:08:43.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像很好吃呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.54,0:09:06.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.43,0:09:22.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚利亚社长…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.03,0:09:29.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚利亚社长！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.78,0:09:39.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子好饱哦 亚利亚社长
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.62,0:09:49.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 肚子饿了 去吃披萨…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.10,0:09:52.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是鬓子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.38,0:09:57.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得的休息日 我还想跟艾莉西亚小姐偶遇的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.62,0:09:59.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不识相的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.25,0:10:04.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉 还是揪揪她的鬓发当作打招呼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.49,0:10:09.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去那边看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.03,0:10:12.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.69,0:10:15.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 去哪了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.52,0:10:22.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.40,0:10:26.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪里在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.87,0:10:29.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪里在哪里在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.40,0:10:35.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪里在哪里…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.51,0:10:40.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟丢了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.79,0:10:44.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大妈 给我一个番茄披萨
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.23,0:10:46.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.32,0:10:50.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢惠顾
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.02,0:10:54.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.29,0:10:59.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚利亚社长 新的洋装到货了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.14,0:11:03.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她在干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.84,0:11:12.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿晓
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.68,0:11:14.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.86,0:11:16.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天你休息吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.61,0:11:18.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.77,0:11:22.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次的中学同窗会阿晓你去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.93,0:11:23.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.76,0:11:26.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就把我们两个的回执寄出去了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.23,0:11:27.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.70,0:11:31.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个披萨好像很不错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.61,0:11:35.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.51,0:11:36.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.36,0:11:38.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 谢谢的说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.94,0:11:43.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她进去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.89,0:11:44.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.69,0:11:45.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.72,0:11:53.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 我的披萨 在哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.12,0:12:05.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很合适哦 太好了呢 亚利亚社长
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.71,0:13:07.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佛洛林咖啡馆的装修开始了哦 亚利亚社长
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.87,0:13:25.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定会变得闪闪发亮的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.46,0:13:31.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又跟丢了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.23,0:13:34.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敏捷的家伙！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.72,0:14:15.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是神出鬼没的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.27,0:14:20.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 门打不开
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.44,0:14:24.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般游客不能从这边进
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.17,0:14:27.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去搭电梯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.53,0:14:28.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.08,0:14:32.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.74,0:14:39.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.58,0:14:41.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用不用 下次再来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.48,0:14:43.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 跟艾莉西亚小姐问好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.59,0:14:44.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.76,0:15:02.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好慢！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.96,0:15:05.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.48,0:15:08.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙…什么时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.74,0:15:12.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼哼哼哼 这次你跑不掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.31,0:15:13.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我觉悟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.42,0:15:18.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 马尾男？他在干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.31,0:15:22.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超级偷偷摸摸的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.29,0:15:23.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 小后辈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.47,0:15:25.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他这是去哪里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.49,0:15:27.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.11,0:15:28.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要跟过去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.29,0:15:30.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.56,0:15:35.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久没来这里了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.29,0:15:40.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为是观光胜地 所以附近人很多
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.13,0:15:44.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但不可思议的是 谁都不会注意到这里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.56,0:15:50.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓝华和爱丽丝 说不定连艾莉西亚前辈都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.47,0:15:53.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只属于我的秘密基地
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.81,0:15:57.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样坐着的话 就没有人会发现我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.61,0:16:01.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚利亚社长
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.87,0:16:04.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新威尼斯的城市
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.08,0:16:07.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也在一点一点地变化着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.46,0:16:13.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.62,0:16:19.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪都找不到上去的楼梯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.77,0:16:21.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.33,0:16:31.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙到底是怎么上去的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.31,0:16:35.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道…是那个？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.13,0:16:41.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没上锁 没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.42,0:16:47.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉 不管了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.99,0:16:57.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.84,0:17:00.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整个寺院一目了然呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.20,0:17:12.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马…屁屁…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.31,0:17:27.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然睡着了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.75,0:17:51.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超级双料鬓发征服！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.81,0:17:54.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道厉害了吧 鬓子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.35,0:17:55.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晓先生…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.89,0:17:57.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偷袭太卑鄙了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.16,0:17:59.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于让我抓住你了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.38,0:18:01.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓住？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.61,0:18:06.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说 为什么本大爷要尾行鬓子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.78,0:18:10.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 这绝不是在尾行！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.60,0:18:13.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过话说回来 你居然能找到这里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.10,0:18:16.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边上楼的楼梯很不起眼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.70,0:18:18.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般人都不会注意到的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.05,0:18:21.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 对本大爷来说是易如反掌
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.24,0:18:25.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 你到这种地方来干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.11,0:18:29.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实这里有一位让我十分在意的人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.74,0:18:34.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我偶尔会偷偷来见他
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.71,0:18:41.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在幽会吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.35,0:18:41.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.06,0:18:44.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有两个人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.50,0:18:45.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.72,0:18:48.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不过亚利亚社长也一起哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.68,0:18:58.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他一直孤单一人 从这里眺望着大海
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.71,0:19:03.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬓子啊 你说的他到底是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.56,0:19:06.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.12,0:19:08.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我问你他是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.09,0:19:13.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这位
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.90,0:19:20.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不说那个了 晓先生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.22,0:19:21.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过来这边
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.47,0:19:22.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.72,0:19:24.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你把头放在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.11,0:19:29.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能跟这位用一样的视线眺望这里的景色了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.93,0:19:37.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.13,0:20:04.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这不变的风景之中
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.04,0:20:13.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仍会有许多高兴的事情 崭新的事情 悲伤的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.45,0:20:15.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些事情堆积起了每个日子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.58,0:20:18.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后慢慢改变着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.50,0:20:24.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像云的形状和海的颜色在变换一样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.28,0:20:26.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安静地…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.45,0:20:33.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这位先生 在不为人知的漫长数百年间
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.02,0:20:38.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直守护着这个广场
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.20,0:20:41.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然非常美好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.48,0:20:44.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却也有点悲伤呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.66,0:20:56.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我啊 把这里当成了我的秘密基地
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.20,0:21:27.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs26}恭喜你们
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.58,0:21:40.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会告诉别人的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.13,0:21:45.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里就是我们的秘密基地了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.34,0:21:47.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本大爷和鬓子的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.64,0:21:58.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有亚利亚社长和那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.46,0:22:04.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.91,0:22:13.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦 无视掉我们 你们继续 继续
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.99,0:22:15.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.95,0:22:17.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰二位了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.82,0:22:19.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是超级路人甲
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.65,0:22:22.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我站住！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.27,0:22:25.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥斯拉 不准误会！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.89,0:22:29.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs26}不要告诉艾莉西亚小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.95,0:22:28.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可是我的秘密基地啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.21,0:22:32.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.02,0:22:38.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天开始 这里变成了大家的秘密基地呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.26,0:22:43.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个城市在长久的不变中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.29,0:22:46.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知不觉地在改变着
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.62,0:22:50.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自己一定也是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.82,0:22:53.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灯里姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.22,0:23:00.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次见面的时候 新威尼斯和灯里姐姐会有些许的变化呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.66,0:23:06.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 莫非我也是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.42,0:23:56.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.47,0:24:00.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀 你回来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.57,0:24:09.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…超级大谜团
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.74,0:24:11.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小后辈 你眼神好认真
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.58,0:24:12.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么谜团啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.88,0:24:14.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「哎呀哎呀 呵呵」的谜团
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.95,0:24:15.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次回
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.77,0:24:17.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那次 精彩的课外教学…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.39,0:24:20.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 请握住我的手
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【OPJP】
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.14,0:01:00.32,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}憶えていますか？ あの日を
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.43,0:01:10.27,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}ふと感じた ときめきを
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.19,0:01:20.36,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}蒼い日差し浴びて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.22,0:01:24.72,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}風を切る君に
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.04,0:01:31.40,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}見とれてると 目が合って
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.52,0:01:36.26,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}笑顔こぼれた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.11,0:01:43.53,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}まるで スピラーレ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.40,0:01:50.31,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,1000)\an7}いつまでも 手を振りたい日々
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.19,0:01:54.60,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}ここに たしかに
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.99,0:02:00.13,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}君といた証
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.88,0:02:04.48,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}ずっと スピラーレ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.89,0:02:14.27,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}この先も 続いてる道がある
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.69,0:02:23.00,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}次の坂を 登ったら
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.79,0:02:27.76,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,1000)}また会いましょう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【OPCH】
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.14,0:01:00.32,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}可曾记得？ 那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.43,0:01:10.27,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}涌上心头的 感动
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.19,0:01:20.36,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}沐浴着湛蓝的阳光
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.22,0:01:24.72,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}你迎风前行的身姿
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.04,0:01:31.40,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}让我陶醉时 目光相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.52,0:01:36.26,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}我们齐声欢笑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.11,0:01:43.53,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}就像那 小小漩涡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.40,0:01:50.31,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,1000)\an3}无论何时 都想挥动双手的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.19,0:01:54.60,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}确实是 曾经
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.99,0:02:00.13,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}与你同在的印记
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.88,0:02:04.48,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}永远如 小小漩涡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.89,0:02:14.27,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}我们的前方 道路在延伸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.69,0:02:23.00,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}攀上 下一个陡坡后
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.79,0:02:27.76,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,1000)}我们再相见吧
