Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.72,0:20:50.01,INCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\an7}如今在那陌生的城市
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.11,0:21:08.25,INCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}钟响之前我决定等待
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.25,0:21:14.76,INCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}他丢下了 最重要的宝物
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.06,0:21:26.31,INCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}丢失了钥匙的鸟笼之梦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.06,0:21:33.14,INCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}他一定会来找寻
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.52,0:21:43.00,INCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\an9}翅膀交错的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.08,0:21:45.93,INCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\an7}漫天的花瓣在飞舞
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.50,0:21:52.14,INCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\an9}想听到的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.08,0:21:56.15,INCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\an7}独自描绘的窗棱
